<!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><i> There are very good, very sound gameplay reasons for this no longer being the case.  Does the manual for a '67 vette tell you everything about a '02 ZR-1?  No, of course not.  Likewise EverQuest is a <!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> very</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--> different game from when it was first released (the manual you are quoting is from the first release).  I'm not unhappy about this at all either.</i><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--><br>
